    • getVariable

      @Deprecated com.guidewire.pl.web.symbol.VariableElement getVariable(String name)
      Deprecated.
      use getPropertyValue(String) to get the value or setPropertyValue(String, Object) to set.

      For example: 

      
  var claim1 = TopLocation.getVariable("Claim").Value
  var claim2 = TopLocation.getPropertyValue("Claim")
  assert(claim1 == claim2)
      Gets the internal VariableElement for the given property.
      Parameters:
      name - the name of the variable.
      Returns:
      the element.
